{"tid":1913101,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"ViuTV奇幻愛情穿越劇《二月廿九》(10)","createTime":"2020-03-06T14:03:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-06T14:05:19.000Z","uid":1130,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc60b881934f7e068d548e5f70604e1ac12423a","tid":1913101,"uid":1130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:03:21.000Z","msg":"《二月廿九》四年一遇 聚散有時<br />\n三位主角 徐天佑、吳海昕、劉俊謙，<br />\n<br />\n免費重溫：<br />\n<a href=\"https://viu.tv/encore/leap-day\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fviu.tv%2Fencore%2Fleap-day&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=7204d61a\" target=\"_blank\">https://viu.tv/encore/leap-day</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MSV6Yzz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMSV6Yzz.jpg&h=19387fef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n預告發放<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2523424837765810/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FViuTV.hk%2Fvideos%2F2523424837765810%2F&d=nExaWN1d7lalHJLKFoHQnGyprV%2B6HEKZLwhfW4p%2FhGU%3D&h=f364efed\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ViuTV.hk/videos/2523424837765810/</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n張麗紗Yeesa（吳海昕 飾），2月29日出生的平凡少女。2017年，Yeesa於2月28日為自己慶祝生日，在11時59分一刻，竟然穿越時空，來到天寒地凍的北海道，過程中遇上和她未來命脈相連的兩個男人－馬智浩Ryan（徐天佑 飾）與餘家聰（劉俊謙 飾），兩個香港男生都不約而同地聲稱與她相識。24小時過去，Yeesa穿越回到香港，現實卻只過了一秒鐘。Yeesa發現自己的穿越能力不由自主，而她竟然在現實裡重新認識Ryan及家聰&hellip;&hellip;命運的齒輪在靜靜地轉動著&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n播放時間<br />\nch.99 星期一至五 21:30"},{"pid":"0fce49b03f0552b14e6d12b5429fa3e3ebba58c0","tid":1913101,"uid":42582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-06T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"來佢自己敲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df7c5b5f3341562cfe6b499cc9197375299d8ba7","tid":1913101,"uid":200245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":